<h3 class="endpoint">
    GET /api/v1/courses/:course_id/activity_stream/summary
  </h3>
<p>Returns a summary of the current user's course-specific activity
stream.</p>
<p>For full documentation, see the API documentation for the user activity
stream summary, in the user api.</p>
